Class Record

  • java.lang.Object
    • bo.Record
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RecordAnalytics, Serializable, Comparable<Record>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    PopulationRecord

    public abstract class Record
extends Object
implements Serializable, RecordAnalytics, Comparable<Record>
    Abstract super class that virtualizes the the generic characteristics of a single row.
    Author:
    Brady Houseknecht
